README thc-ipv6


ABOUT
=====

According to this thread
https://github.com/vanhauser-thc/thc-ipv6/pull/18 van Hauser has a sane
reasons to decline this PR.  And at the same time, since this patch is very
handyful, we may include it as a separate tool to not break backward
compatibility.


